					<description><![CDATA[My lovely little darling has been in the world for 7 years, today.  That is, I started writing the series on Nov 17th, 2010.  And now, all 12 books are written, 6 are published, and my Twist isn’t just mine anymore.  I just love the idea that he’s met more people than I ever could. [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2966" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Twist-BDay-2017-7years-old-sm.jpg" alt="Twist BDay 2017 7years old sm" width="667" height="500" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Twist-BDay-2017-7years-old-sm.jpg 667w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Twist-BDay-2017-7years-old-sm-300x224.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Twist-BDay-2017-7years-old-sm-618x463.jpg 618w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Twist-BDay-2017-7years-old-sm-138x104.jpg 138w" sizes="(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px" /></p>
<p>My lovely little darling has been in the world for 7 years, today.  That is, I started writing the series on Nov 17th, 2010.  And now, all 12 books are written, 6 are published, and my Twist isn’t just mine anymore.  I just love the idea that he’s met more people than I ever could.</p>
<p>So raise a glass, or grab a cupcake, in honor of Twist today!  As my gift to all of you, the first book in the series, <a href="http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FClockwork-Twist-Waking-Emily-Thompson-ebook%2Fdp%2FB00BXKXCUQ&amp;t=NjRlODNjYTU1NDM2MjQ3MGJjNTk2Y2ZmMzk1MDBmZjE2ZDE2YzM0NixnZFFhOWUxQQ%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3AB0JpR0rXyCqKf6vxyfvgZg&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fcwtwist.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F167597619247%2Fhappy-birthday-twist-my-lovely-little-darling&amp;m=1" target="_blank">Clockwork Twist : Waking</a> will be free on Amazon Kindle all day!  Tell your friends, or get a free copy of the ebook for yourself, if you haven’t already got one.</p>
<p>Also, as promised, the 6th book is out right now!  If you’re caught up with the rest of the series, head over to my site (<a href="http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fclockworktwist.com%2Fblood%2F&amp;t=MWVkMTRjZjJlYjFiYmFkOTRkYzYyYzU5MjVhZWFkOTRhMTFkNjZlNixnZFFhOWUxQQ%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3AB0JpR0rXyCqKf6vxyfvgZg&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fcwtwist.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F167597619247%2Fhappy-birthday-twist-my-lovely-little-darling&amp;m=1" target="_blank">http://clockworktwist.com/blood/</a>) to read the first three chapters, or go and pick up a fresh new copy on <a href="http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB077GHTNDX%2F&amp;t=ODRjNjY2Mzc0Y2I5YWYxZjZiMDgxNzMxNGEwYzdmYzI0MjJiYzljNCxnZFFhOWUxQQ%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3AB0JpR0rXyCqKf6vxyfvgZg&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fcwtwist.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F167597619247%2Fhappy-birthday-twist-my-lovely-little-darling&amp;m=1" target="_blank">Amazon</a> and follow Twist through another fantastic adventure.</p>
<p>Thank you all for all of your interest and support!  Here’s to another year!’</p>
<p>Book One, Free today <a href="http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FClockwork-Twist-Waking-Emily-Thompson-ebook%2Fdp%2FB00BXKXCUQ&amp;t=NjRlODNjYTU1NDM2MjQ3MGJjNTk2Y2ZmMzk1MDBmZjE2ZDE2YzM0NixnZFFhOWUxQQ%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3AB0JpR0rXyCqKf6vxyfvgZg&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fcwtwist.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F167597619247%2Fhappy-birthday-twist-my-lovely-little-darling&amp;m=1" target="_blank">https://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Waking-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00BXKXCUQ</a></p>
<p>Book Six, Available today <a href="http://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB077GHTNDX&amp;t=NDczNTUyYjVkYzgyMjgxODcxZjQ0MWVjNDI5M2U3MGNmYzRiMTVmNyxnZFFhOWUxQQ%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3AB0JpR0rXyCqKf6vxyfvgZg&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fcwtwist.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F167597619247%2Fhappy-birthday-twist-my-lovely-little-darling&amp;m=1" target="_blank">https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B077GHTNDX</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
